metadata.name: WHO IS THE DEVIL?
metadata.description:
A woman wants to express herself, that she has been able to destroy a tiger that has majestic, handsome, powerful, mighty, fast, strong, beautiful, and exotic traits. But on the other hand, when she wants to express himself by tattooing his body, A man who wants to have his body tattooed is being influenced by the devil, which a devil is everyone's enemy.

Will the man be able to destroy the devil, like a woman who has destroyed a tiger?
But what is the true nature of the devil?
Who is the real devil, and why does everyone want to destroy him?

Hand-drawn illustration 4000 x 4000 pixel created by Taufan Bagus D. P. A
